Airlines Hotel
Mood Board

Project Overview

A structured approach to defining the visual language for the Airlines Hotel coffee table book.

01

Understanding the Content

Exploring the rich heritage and stories that define Airlines Hotel - from its founding history to the vibrant community it serves today.

02

Technical Considerations

Print specifications, paper selection, binding methods, and production requirements that will influence design decisions.

03

Defining Style

Two distinct mood board options presenting different visual directions - color palettes, typography, layout approaches, and photographic treatments.

Understanding the Content

The book content is organized into two thematic pillars, each telling a different facet of the Airlines Hotel story.

Theme 1

Heritage & Foundation

  • About Airlines Hotel
  • About SNS Rao
  • Diwakar Rao
  • B&W Old Photographs
Theme 2

Community & Stories

  • Hostel
  • Corner House
  • Families
  • Bikers
  • Food and Kitchen
  • Staff Profiles
  • LGBTQ
  • Pets
  • Parent-Child
  • Friends
